combat_hint=Use $ATTACK to perform a normal attack. Use $SMASH to perform a heavy attack.\nYou can chain attacks together to create melee combos.\nEXAMPLE: $ATTACK,$ATTACK,$SMASH = Pop-up Attack\n\nYou can also [left click] on an enemy to normal attack or [right click] to heavy attack. Holding down the mouse button allows for a continuous attack until the enemy's death.
break_hint=Sometimes you can find useful items by breaking open crates and barrels.  \n\nTry punching these crates to break them open.\n\nYou can hold $ATTACKOBJ and [left click] or [right click] to attack an object.  Holding the mouse button allows for a continuous attack.
automap_hint=The Automap shows your current position, and also uses various icons to show you the locations of mission objectives and other important objects.\n\nTap $MAPTOGGLE to cycle through the Automap's three settings:  Small, Large, and Hidden.

