power_tut_x=Press and hold $POWER, then press the character selection buttons.  Each of the 4 directions correspond to one of the power buttons.  Each press of the character selection keys cycles to the next available power for that button.


power_hint=If you hold down $POWER, you can choose $GUARD,$MOVE,$ATTACK, or $SMASH to activate a mutant power. You can also use the shortcut keys like $POWER1,$POWER2 or $POWER3 to activate a power directly. While holding $BINDPOWER, you can assign the left and right mouse buttons to specific powers. Then to use the powers, [left click] or [right click] while holding $USEQKPOWER.\n\nUsing mutant powers drains some of your Energy.  In the corner of your screen, the blue bar next to your Active Hero's head indicates how much Mutant Energy you have left. Use $ALLY to replenish your Energy with Energy Packs. You can also [left click] on the item in the hud.
switching_hint=Press $DPAD_UP,$DPAD_DN,$DPAD_LF or $DPAD_RT to choose which of your teammates will become your active hero.\n\nEXAMPLE:\nPress $DPAD_LF = Wolverine\nPress $DPAD_RT = Cyclops\nPress $DPAD_DN = Storm\nPress $DPAD_UP = Magneto\n\nYou can also [left click] on them to switch while holding $SWTHERO or, simply [left click] on the head displayed in the hud.
potion_hint=Getting hit by enemies drains some of your Health.  In the corner of your screen, the red bar next to your Active Hero's head indicates how much Health you have left.\n\nPress $TARGET_LOCK to replenish your Health with Health Packs or you can [left click] on the icon in the hud.


